  <br>
  <p class="landingLogin"><a href="/login">Login</a></p>
  <div class="container">
  <div class="logo">
    <img class="logoImg" src="coffeehouselogo.png">
    <h1 class="logoText text-left mt-5">Coffee House</h1>
    <h2 class="logoDescription text-left">Compose, collaborate, and explore a growing library of open-source music.</h2>
    <div class="buttonWrapper mt-5">
      <a href="/signup"><button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Sign Up</button></a>
      <a href="/home"><button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-lg ml-3 ">Explore</button></a>
  </div>
  </div>
</div>

</div>
<div class="features">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="rows">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-2 col-md-offset mt-5">
          <i class="fa fa-5x fa-pencil" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-10 col-sm-10 mt-5">
          <h3>Compose</h3>
          <p>Share your music with the world. Start by uploading a single sound file, and build upon your creation by iteratively adding additional sounds clips using a git-style interface. Track changes and gain a bird's-eye view of how your creation develops. </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row mt-5">
        <div class="col-md-10">
          <h3>Collaborate</h3>
          <p>Invite your friends to help you improve your track, or watch as strangers you've never met layer their own work on top of yours. All iterations are stored seperately allowing for complete control over your music.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-2 col-md-offset">
          <i class="fa fa-5x fa-users" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row mt-5">
        <div class="col-2 col-md-offset">
          <i class="fa fa-5x fa-desktop" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-10">
          <h3>Explore</h3>
          <p>Browse a growing library of open-source music. Keep up with your favourite tracks and watch as they progress. Clone your favourite tracks to branch off and put your own rendition on your favourite tracks.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="buttonWrapper mt-5">
      <a href="/home"><button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-lg">Get Started</button></a>
  </div>
